l-Programming-Jargon\">Functional Programming Jargon</a> - Explains terms used in functional programming in the JavaScript context.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-08T20:17:41.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles &#x26; Tutorials</h2><h3>Overall Topics</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://javascript.info\">JavaScript.info</a> - A modern tutorial from the basics to advanced topics with simple, but detailed explanations.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-06-22T13:20:56.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Node.js</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://learnnode.com\">Learn Node</a> - A premium training course to learn to build apps with Node.js, Express, MongoDB.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-06-12T22:49:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>ES6 and above</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mjavascript/practical-es6\">Practical ES6</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mjavascript/practical-es6\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.9k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2873,\"repo\":\"mjavascript/practical-es6\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - eBook with practical examples and advices.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-02-15T20:07:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>JavaScript References</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ecma-international.org/publications/standards/Ecma-262.htm\">ECMAScript® Language Specification</a> - The standard JavaScript is based on. Only for very advanced learners.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-01-22T11:20:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Node.js</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a